These are Puzzles for 4x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x7-Level-2-1::.
There 7 different types of food: garlic, artichoke, cranberry, lime, lettuce, papaya, cucumber
The people have 7 different hobbies: fishing, skydiving, collecting, board-games, puzzles, card-games, rock-climbing
7 different brands of cigars are smoked: bolivar, pall-mall, aristoff, alhambra, game, siglo, bongani
There are 7 different favourite colors: ivory, fuchsia, white, brown, blood-red, mauve, turquise
 1. the alhambra-smoker is on the far right##1
 2. the game-smoker is the person who's hobby is board-games##1
 3. the person who likes blood-red is the aristoff-smoker##1
 4. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left of the person who likes mauve##1
 5. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
 6. the person eating artichoke is the aristoff-smoker##1
 7. the person who likes turquise is on the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
 8. the person who likes brown is between the person who likes turquise and the person who's hobby is card-games##2
 9. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the right of the person who likes white##1
10. the person eating cranberry is in the middle##1
11. the bolivar-smoker is the person eating lettuce##1
12. the person eating lettuce is the person who likes ivory##1
13. the person eating garlic is on the left of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
14. the person who's hobby is card-games is the person who likes white##1
15. the person who likes mauve is on the left of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
16. the person eating artichoke is on the left of the person eating papaya##1
17. the siglo-smoker is on the left of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
18. the person eating cucumber is on the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
19. the bongani-smoker is on the right of the person who likes fuchsia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |    3     |     4      |     5     |    6     |    7    |
| Food      | artichoke  | papaya        | lettuce | cranberry      | lime     | garlic      | cucumber     |
| Hobby   | skydiving | board-games         | rock-climbing   | fishing | card-games    | puzzles | collecting |
| Cigar         | aristoff | game | bolivar | pall-mall | bongani  | siglo  | alhambra    |
| Color     | blood-red  | mauve         | ivory     | fuchsia    | white | brown     | turquise     |

