 9. the person traveling to prague is on the left of the pilot##1
10. the person playing canasta is between the person playing mah-jongg and the person who growstulip##2
11. the person playing whist is the person who growsbellflower##1
12. the person playing snooker is on the left of the person playing domino##1
13. the person playing snooker is between the person who growstulip and the person playing domino##2
